      "label": "Memory Stress Testing Best Practices [chunk 3/4]",
      "type": "fact",
      "tier": "training",
      "content": "k that training materials get confidence=0.95.\n\n6. FAILOVER: Kill the sidecar mid-operation and verify the HTTP API falls back to LiveMemorySync keyword search. Restart the sidecar and verify it re-indexes.\n\n7. ENTITY LINKING: Write two nodes with shared entities and verify a relation is created between them. Search by entity should return both nodes.\n\n8. TEMPORAL INVALIDATION: Write a fact, then write a contradicting fact about the same entity. The old fact should get validUntil set.",
